I'm Nep — a software developer, writer, and lifelong learner based in the US. I build things for the web and write about the process.

I'm passionate about clean code, developer experience, and making technology more accessible. When I'm not coding, you'll find me reading, listening to podcasts, or exploring new ideas.

This site is my home on the web — a place to share my work, writing, and recommendations.
